data.description: WELCOME HOME! This home is BETTER THAN NEW and sits on one of the best streets and lots within the master-planned neighborhood of Kinston that is within the highly desired area of Centerra located in Loveland. Offering exceptional value and fully transferable builder warranties, this home comes complete with landscaping and a state of the art security system and so much more! It boasts the perfect blend of luxury and comfort that makes it a must have! As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by an elegant foyer that sets the tone for the rest of this impeccable home. The spacious and open concept floorplan is flooded with lots of storage and natural sunlight along with featuring 5 beds/3 baths with an oversized 2 car garage that includes an unfinished basement. The main floor is exceptional for entertaining with the kitchen flowing into the living room and dining area that is completed with a bedroom/office and a full bath. Meanwhile, the upper floor offers a seamless blend of comfort and functionality with a large loft area along with 4 additional bedrooms and 2 baths. The basement is the best kept secret, as many of the homes in the neighborhood don't have them. Buyers will have the ability to expand and create the finishing touches at their leisure when completing the basement. The backyard oasis has been professionally landscaped and is adjacent to open space that is expected to include walking trails, natural habitats and award-winning botanic and sculpture gardens. Kinston in Centerra is a unique, new community that includes "The Hub" where residents enjoy the local brewery that is now open along with a future swimming pool, workout facilities, splash pad, concerts on the lawn and so much more. Located conveniently near I-25 and Hwy 34 along with easy access to Loveland, Johnstown, Windsor, Greeley, and Fort Collins. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own this exceptional home!
